Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The year 1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}DÃ¼sseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the beginning of this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:17.12,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(210,360)}Dr. Kenzo Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure, 72/50.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulse, 137.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So the bullet entered his skull from the front...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We need X-rays immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the twin sister of that boy just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't your operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mayor, Mr. Roedecker, has collapsed\Nfrom a cerebral thrombosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was about to start the\Noperation on that child!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an order from the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have him die yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.33,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Director Heinemann
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:04.77,Default,,0,0,80,,I'm counting on you, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect a great deal from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you better make preparations, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're relying on those brilliant skills of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They think doctors are some\Nkind of volunteers or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even before saving lives,\Nwe doctors value academics first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I merely operated on that opera singer\Nlike the director told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not my fault
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because people's lives aren't equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only you had operated on him,\Nhe would have survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give him back! Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an operation waiting for me in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Dr. Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order from the director!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.10,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,320)}The Beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure, 128/72.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulse, 88.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there are still some residual\Neffects from the anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it went smoothly on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After going against the director's orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tenma was removed from his position\Nas chief neurosurgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and his engagement to the director's \Ndaughter, Eva, was cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for someone with\Nan attitude problem, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The path of being the doctor you \Ndreamed of is closed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.76,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Eva Heinemann
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.61,Default,,0,0,85,,You really are a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell with all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Director's orders my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief's orders my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All they care about are money\Nand their stupid positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for disturbing you so\Nearly in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from the county police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:06:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that Director Heinemann, Surgical Director\NOppenheim, and Dr. Boyer of Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,have all passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find them anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell... happened here...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm appointing you as the head\Nof the surgical department.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What a life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What a life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The deaths of Director Heinemann and two\Nothers at Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:23.33,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,750)\pos(360,300)}9 Years Later
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The disappearance of the twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, nine years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new incident occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster... is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same as back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poisoned by candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My patient disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is just like what happened nine years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my life nine years ago, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably already forgot\Nabout those two little twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in that position today because the director,\Nhead surgeon, and chief are dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it when I regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You hated them so much that\Nyou wanted to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I only did what you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have died back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But you brought me back to life, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.70,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}Inspector Lunge
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's let him go for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After the murders at Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see only one person who benefited from the\Nincident, no matter how much I think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma, you're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who brought that\Nmonster... back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow at 7pm, on the night of your birthday,\Nwe'll meet at Heidelberg Castle."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At Heidelberg Castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:10.85,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(625,625)\pos(360,300)}Heidelberg
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Papa. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got off work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:18.74,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(375,0)}Nina Fortner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:13.91,Default,,0,0,90,,I'm going to meet up with a friend now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,90,,{\i1}Johan's twin sister, Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,90,,{\i1}had lost her memory after the\Nincident nine years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, at Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and was living with foster parents in Heidelberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She called herself Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On her twentieth birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she received an anonymous email...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and headed for Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way past the time we were supposed to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was a prank after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're Nina Fortner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Doctor Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He said no one would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When did he say he was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He only said that he'll come here after he's\Ntaken care of something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry back to your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mauler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed my brother back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, those who are kind to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...everyone of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...just dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But on that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...I finally found out why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,On that rainy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother shot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He... shot all of those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... I picked up the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I aimed it at my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was laughing when he said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He said to aim straight for his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you hadn't saved my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa and Mama wouldn't have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell the police about the necktie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them that the incident where my father and the others were killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...was all your fault too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Close off all entrances to the ward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the rear entrances as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's a huge commotion over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of police cars out there, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please drop me off in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're busy as usual Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma, it's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You only performed your duty as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not your fault
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please eat the sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And please, get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And... please save as many lives as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:13.44,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,320)}5 Months Later
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tenma was on the run as\Na suspect in the murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, that was the beginning of the\Nlong journey to hunt down Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They said another middle-aged couple\Nwas murdered, this time in Verden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They said a doctor did it, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, you said you were\Ngoing to Verden, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know someone living\Nthere or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll meet him there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.81,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(360,310)}Berlin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to ask\Nme about those twins, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a good deal about her brother, Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I want to ask you about Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That was top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Johan do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He led a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Every member of the orphanage,\Nincluding the instructors...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,killed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The instructors, and even the orphans...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All fifty took their last breath here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He just gazed upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan just gazed upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked him just what he had done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And he answered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hatred is born when people gather together."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"I merely poured some oil onto this."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy of only ten years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And he did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He made fifty people kill each other without\Nlifting one finger of his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't what Johan wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:33.71,ScreenTxt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}Frankfurt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.43,Default,,0,0,100,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,100,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the place he indicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan didn't wish for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't wish for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the kind of person you think he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's much more complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's much more frightening than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... writhing in pain in an abyss of grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't shoot people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Johan's message!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when I shot Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally figured out why he wanted\Nme to shoot him in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two Johans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... it's not your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,aim at Johan's head, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leaving numerous mysteries behind him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Johan disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is his goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tenma and Nina's journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hasn't come to an end yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Help me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster inside me is about to explode!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, inside Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there are two personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:36.79,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And slowly, you come to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:44.38,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all as it should be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.81,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can only do so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:59.40,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you're game enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:07.20,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You could place your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:16.29,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For the love of life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:21.63,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's a trade off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:28.39,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We could lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:33.31,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But we'll go down fighting

